    "en": {
      "title": "Now the petrol stations are controlled by the underworld",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Power and Energy Minister Mr. Kanchana Wijesekera says that the underworld is doing this at the fuel stations.",
        "In a press conference held in Colombo today, he mentioned that the Ceylon Petroleum Corporation is issuing fuel to fuel stations and the responsibility for distributing the fuel thus provided is to each fuel station.",
        "Also, in the last 10 days, no fuel has been released to Cipetco fuel stations, but there are still a significant number of vehicles on the roads."
      ],
